### 1. 用户注册
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "测试用户"
}

### 2. 获取所有用户
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/list

### 3. 创建TODO备忘项
POST http://localhost:8080/api/item
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "type": "TODO",
  "title": "完成作业",
  "content": "数学作业第3章",
  "config": "{\"deadline\":\"2025-11-05\",\"priority\":\"high\",\"progress\":{\"current\":2,\"total\":5}}"
}

### 4. 创建HABIT备忘项
POST http://localhost:8080/api/item
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "type": "HABIT",
  "title": "每天喝8杯水",
  "config": "{\"repeat_rule\":\"daily\",\"streak_days\":0}"
}

### 5. 获取用户1的所有备忘项
GET http://localhost:8080/api/item/user/1

### 6. 切换备忘项状态
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/item/1/toggle

### 7. 注册设备
POST http://localhost:8080/api/device/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "deviceName": "书桌屏幕",
  "deviceToken": "test-token-123456",
  "macAddress": "AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:FF"
}

### 8. 设备认证测试
GET http://localhost:8080/api/device/auth/test-token-123456